Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:40.46,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊擁抱 心靈的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.61,0:00:46.82,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱情燃燒 創造奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:52.19,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能就這樣受著傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.26,0:00:58.42,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相發誓過的 遙遠的銀河
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.15,0:01:04.69,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬座的幻想 只有夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.09,0:01:10.70,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也奪不走 因為是心靈的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.94,0:01:16.64,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 少年都是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.68,0:01:20.82,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 明天的勇士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.56,0:01:28.28,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 就像天馬座
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.31,0:01:35.94,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 現在就展開羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.75,0:00:35.11,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光荣字幕组&galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.72,0:00:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當邪惡在此世蔓延之時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會現身的希望之戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身著星座之聖衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆發蘊藏在身體中的能量「小宇宙」進行著戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.17,0:00:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們正是 保護大地上愛與和平的戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.95,0:00:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士光牙尋找雅典娜的旅程還在繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.52,0:01:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸為了奪回阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.46,0:01:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於發揮出了他那壓倒性的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙雖受阿莉雅庇護得以保全性命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.23,0:01:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻因這屈辱的敗戰而消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.46,0:02:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸在光牙的面前帶走了阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.73,0:02:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年們啊 燃燒內心的小宇宙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法飛翔的天馬！從喪失中的再啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙 振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙 光牙！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少管我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.33,0:02:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你還活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.21,0:02:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我輸了 才讓阿莉雅被…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓阿莉雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:02:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙織小姐！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.24,0:03:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候落下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:04:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 那是我以前送給你的耳環
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.23,0:04:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都戴著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 又要讓你被關在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親來了 快去稟報吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.23,0:04:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若她不是雅典娜 早就將其拋棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好受點了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去你現在需要去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 到底去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟來你就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 您能親來助戰 吾等萬分榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看來你也平安無恙吶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次伊甸平安地把我們的雅典娜 阿莉雅帶回
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 做得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新聖域也即將建成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.71,0:05:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.32,0:05:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事想向您請教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:05:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要將Palaestra變成那副樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.23,0:06:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要用黑暗之力把美麗的大地變得醜陋不堪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸你還真是溫柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要知道 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.92,0:06:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的地球正處在再生的痛苦之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森林燃盡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海污濁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空狂躁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此 巴比倫塔才會在此拔地而起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.00,0:06:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了創造我們嶄新的地球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 現在經歷些許災殃也是迫不得已的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新聖域是為了迎接你這位王而建成的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要為一些瑣碎小事而分心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有一事相求
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於將與我一起守護新世界的阿莉雅的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望父親您現在能給予阿莉雅一些自由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.93,0:07:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來忘記自身使命的阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.13,0:07:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就應該被永遠囚禁於黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對此不予過問 父親已是寬大之至
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今引導年輕不成熟的雅典娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對她進行教育指導才是你的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要搞錯了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽到我的話了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你將成為新世界的王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要知道 你的這份溫柔就等同於軟弱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軟弱…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不軟弱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤娜 你要帶我去哪兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是過去我為了得到聖衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歷盡艱苦修業 捨棄軟弱的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慟哭之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.37,0:08:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要帶我來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是個膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為你是個膽小鬼 阿莉雅才會被擄走！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧 光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本無能為力啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.47,0:08:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無能為力？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是瑪爾斯的兒子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的實力相差太多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不可能戰勝他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙你這個大笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛突然出拳啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你那副自怨自艾的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太沒出息了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為你這副德行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒能保護好雅典娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜 沙織小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會輸 並不是因為對手太強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是你自己太弱了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.74,0:09:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不想去變得更強 去救阿莉雅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不像光牙你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼可能明白 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤娜你怎麼可能明白我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙織小姐被擄走 阿莉雅被擄走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要之人兩次在眼前被人擄走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而無能為力的我的心情！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何 你覺得只有自己受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於我來說 阿莉雅也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是重要的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少管我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅的事也是 沙織小姐的事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已無能為力了 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無能為力了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是慟哭之谷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來你會發生什麼 我也無從知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你將在此處與自己進行戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪爾斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在害怕什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.29,0:11:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你的囈語中聽來似乎是個女人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.18,0:12:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.34,0:12:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想著你會高興的 就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.78,0:12:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看看你戴著它露出的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.48,0:12:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅 這個人是你珍視之人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經再也見不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和你沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟是誰啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這裡到底是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛問這些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我也曾有珍視之人存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的處境並非無法見到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而只是自己不去見罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說得輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.96,0:13:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然知道 包括你想要放棄你所珍視之人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想著與去戰鬥相比 放棄要更為容易
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是這樣沒種的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.91,0:13:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想通過放棄來逃避自身的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.90,0:13:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.13,0:14:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想什麼 阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也沒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.59,0:14:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅 為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖域不久便將完成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.53,0:14:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會成為雅典娜 而我將成為地球的王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅 再忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不了多久 一個如我們所願的世界就會誕生了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會得到完全的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在和他們一起的旅途中究竟發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也沒有 什麼也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:15:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有奢華的餐宴 也沒有柔軟的床鋪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道為什麼 我卻很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和天馬座他們一起的旅途你竟會感到這麼愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你理解一下我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的小宇宙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:15:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼渺小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.67,0:16:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑這種程度的小宇宙 誰也守護不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的小宇宙才不是這點程度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.64,0:16:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬流星拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那片魔傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人失望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣的小宇宙別說是雅典娜　
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本連自身都難保
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓你見識一下 我的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.97,0:17:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 這小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼強大 與我的小宇宙簡直是天壤之別
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想保護他人的話　
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.55,0:17:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就試著燃燒這種程度的小宇宙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過你也有珍視之人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人現在在哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所珍視之人 就在無法觸及的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你所珍視之人已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.85,0:17:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯 她安靜地沉睡在一個永遠也無法相見的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你所珍視之人卻不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:17:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你去見 就會見到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如今的你卻不想去見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想去救出阿莉雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.65,0:18:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拿出你真正的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就燃燒你真正的小宇宙吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.82,0:18:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是聖鬥士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要相信自己的力量　
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.62,0:18:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信自己的小宇宙！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.94,0:18:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就以你心中希望的光芒　
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來承受我小宇宙的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.41,0:18:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你的小宇宙無法承受我的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.58,0:18:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待著你的唯有一死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.88,0:19:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑽石星塵（DIAMOND DUST）！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想救出阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果做得到的話 如果我真的有那力量的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信自己的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.63,0:19:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.92,0:19:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.73,0:20:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒吧 我真正的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒到盡頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.64,0:20:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小宇宙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 天馬 去吧 光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.40,0:20:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他知道我的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.69,0:20:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的同伴正在等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.71,0:21:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.35,0:21:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅 你有什麼願望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的願望就是 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶我去雷之遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.98,0:21:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 尤娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:22:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙 你回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.83,0:22:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我已經不會再迷惘了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.04,0:22:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我不放棄 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.73,0:22:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定能夠救出阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.33,0:22:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我 一定會戰勝伊甸的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.93,0:22:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與同伴分離 回到故鄉的榮斗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.28,0:22:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是潛藏於世間的忍者之村
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.64,0:22:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在直面過往的回憶時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.01,0:22:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榮斗的內心浮現出曾改變自己命運的忍者的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.64,0:22:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者與聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.84,0:22:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時踏上兩條道路的男人究竟將何去何從
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.38,0:22:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話 聖鬥士星矢Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.95,0:22:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對友人的思念！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.23,0:22:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍道與聖鬥士的矜持！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.75,0:22:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾感受到小宇宙的存在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.69,0:23:08.82,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集、榮鬥的過去將要浮出水面！？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.69,0:23:08.82,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榮斗是忍者？還是聖鬥士？
